{"tid":685826,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(香港隊)電競亞運  代表遴選中！Toyz做教練","createTime":"2018-05-31T17:16:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-31T17:28:10.000Z","uid":80775,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3e2b031ea4796083be1246ea69de2ca0f9d1ac48","tid":685826,"uid":80775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T17:16:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://s.newtalk.tw/album/news/127/5b0fd5b3e779f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.newtalk.tw%2Falbum%2Fnews%2F127%2F5b0fd5b3e779f.jpg&h=bd4b7d92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://s.newtalk.tw/album/news/127/5b0fd7eec6200.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.newtalk.tw%2Falbum%2Fnews%2F127%2F5b0fd7eec6200.jpg&h=2e1f7311&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n為了要籌組最棒的電競代表隊，各賽區可以說是都卯足了全力，香港賽區也不例外，今年亞運電競籌委會主席是香港電子競技有限公司（HKE）創辦人鍾培生，表示會以最有效率並且最公平的方式，選出最合適代表香港區的選手。而目前僅確定《英雄聯盟》和《傳說對決》的教練人選分別由Toyz和紅豆擔任，而其他名單日後將會繼續公布。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://newtalk.tw/news/view/2018-05-31/126340\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewtalk.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2F2018-05-31%2F126340&d=fx7eY9BJwtcE%2BbVEeyPzS5UWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=9589b237\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://newtalk.tw/news/view/2018-05-31/126340</a>"},{"pid":"358d071508edb43f6204ec4965022c412272e94e","tid":685826,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T17:19:00.000Z","msg":"香港打機教練"},{"pid":"945b6060d243a4deb040c8be5bcfdab8dcd33f7a","tid":685826,"uid":125419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T17:21:49.000Z","msg":"個記者icon好似幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de4e75293a7eac7b7ca011791fbb3980929a90ef","tid":685826,"uid":80775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T17:23:32.000Z","msg":"電競納入亞運 Faker：非常有意義 <br />\n<br />\n南韓公布了本屆亞運電競代表選手名單，SKT中路大魔王Faker自然也在其列。<br />\n<br />\nSKT的當家王牌中路選手「Faker」李相赫年紀輕輕，卻是令許多選手聞風喪膽的存在，暱稱大魔王的他自然被選作國家代表隊，今日他接受了韓媒Inven的訪問，對於電競項目納為示範項目，Faker表示這是別具意義的里程碑：「這是一次非常有意義的賽事，因為電子競技向那些不喜歡遊戲的人更近了一步。很高興能夠參加這樣的比賽。」"},{"pid":"86cea87c98f21b68b9a79c1efbdf6813d4a3a98a","tid":685826,"uid":61675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T17:23:56.000Z","msg":"時也命也 靚仔又贏過冠軍<br />\n我個人覺得好過咩星之子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cba893e6573a1774116cc979e929136116741e5f","tid":685826,"uid":42609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"945b6060d243a4deb040c8be5bcfdab8dcd33f7a","tid":685826,"uid":125419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T17:21:49.000Z","msg":"個記者icon好似幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T17:28:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/TrySoHardToBeNice\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FTrySoHardToBeNice&d=fx7eY9BJwtcE%2BbVEeyPzS5UWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=e2d849e7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/TrySoHardToBeNice</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}